{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Chaos Machina is a fast-paced Action RPG dungeon crawler with roguelike elements. After a super-intelligent AI discovered chaos magic, the world has gone to s***. You play as the unlucky bastard who is assigned to fix it.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You run into procedurally generated dungeons and fight robots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You need to move to dodge all the enemies ahead of you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies drop randomized items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You need to be quick with your runs otherwise Chaos will consume the dungeon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a successful run, you get permanent upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight against complicated fully simulated enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Replayable gameplay, dungeons change, your abilities change, your enemies change</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become OP as possible to tame Chaos!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406570/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739485565","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406570/page.bg.jpg?t=1739485565","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406570/7dd0ba73ff5bce725b72cf41d94215ed806892dc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739485565","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406570/7dd0ba73ff5bce725b72cf41d94215ed806892dc/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739485565","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Chaos Machina is a fast-paced Action RPG dungeon crawler with roguelike elements. After a super-intelligent AI